    {
      "turn_id": 1,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "propose",
      "utterance": "我们需要画一个工业物联网的流程图，核心是从PLC逻辑开始，然后有个遥测数据流的判断节点。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "IoT_Industrial_PLC_Logic",
        "IoT_Industrial_TelemetryStream"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 2,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "clarify",
      "utterance": "明白了，PLC逻辑作为起点，然后连到遥测数据流的判断节点。这个判断节点是菱形还是矩形？",
      "elements_involved": [
        "IoT_Industrial_PLC_Logic",
        "IoT_Industrial_TelemetryStream"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 3,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "confirm",
      "utterance": "判断节点用菱形，因为这是决策点。如果遥测数据正常，就走到执行器控制器；不正常的话要循环处理。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "IoT_Industrial_TelemetryStream",
        "IoT_Industrial_ActuatorController"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 4,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "execute",
      "utterance": "好的，我画好了：PLC逻辑矩形指向遥测判断菱形，然后分出两条路径。Yes分支到执行器控制器，No分支我暂时画到另一个遥测节点。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "IoT_Industrial_PLC_Logic",
        "IoT_Industrial_TelemetryStream",
        "IoT_Industrial_ActuatorController"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 5,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "repair",
      "utterance": "等等，No分支不能直接结束，需要循环回判断节点重新检测，直到数据正常为止。那个D节点其实就是个处理过程，要指回B。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "IoT_Industrial_TelemetryStream",
        "loop"
      ],
      "is_repair": true
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 6,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "execute",
      "utterance": "修复好了，现在No分支从D节点有回线连回到B判断节点，形成循环结构。这样直到遥测数据正常才会走出去。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "IoT_Industrial_TelemetryStream",
        "loop"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 7,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "propose",
      "utterance": "执行器控制器之后还需要一个最终的遥测数据流节点，用来表示数据上报完成。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "IoT_Industrial_ActuatorController",
        "IoT_Industrial_TelemetryStream"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 8,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "confirm",
      "utterance": "确认一下，C执行器控制器指向E遥测数据流，这个E和前面的B、D是同一类节点吗？",
      "elements_involved": [
        "IoT_Industrial_ActuatorController",
